# CLAUDE.md

This file provides guidance to Claude (and other agents) when working in this repository.

## Project Overview
- App: Flaco AI (CLI + macOS desktop)
- Focus: Local-first AI coding assistant powered by Ollama
- Tech Stack: Python CLI (`flaco/`), Electron UI (`flaco-macos/`)

## Development Commands

### CLI
- Install: `python -m venv venv && source venv/bin/activate && pip install -e .`
- Run: `flaco` or `python -m flaco.cli --help`
- Tests: `pytest`

### Desktop
- Install: `cd flaco-macos && npm install`
- Run: `npm start`
- Tests: `npm test`
- Build: `npm run build:quiet` (CI-safe)

## Conventions
- Python: PEP 8, 4-space indent, type hints where useful; prefer `logging` over prints.
- JavaScript: CommonJS modules, camelCase, renderer-safe code lives in `preload.js`.
- Docs: Customer-facing guides in `docs/guides/`; internal/owner docs in `docs/internal/`.

